# Training outputs (checkpoints, logs, saved configs) go here.
# This directory is git-ignored. Only this .gitkeep file is tracked.
#
# Structure after training:
#   outputs/
#   └── dino_ixi/
#       ├── config.yaml              ← Resolved config snapshot
#       ├── checkpoint.pt            ← Latest checkpoint (auto-resume)
#       ├── checkpoint_epoch=0010.pt ← Periodic checkpoints
#       └── logs/                    ← WandB logs (if enabled)
